name: Neon
description:
The Other Side of Town Beyond the heavily guarded walls of the town lies a world of hedonistic pleasure and danger. Zone 6 is a place where the rules are different, and the nights never end. A neon-lit playground for those who seek to escape the monotony of their controlled lives, it's a place where anything can happen. But beneath the surface lies a dark underbelly of crime and corruption, and those who enter Zone 6 must navigate a world of deception and treachery. Will you succumb to the temptations of the night, or will you uncover the truth behind the glittering fa√ßade?
